est, euh, de guérir avec amour.

116
00:04:14,036 --> 00:04:15,863
Ok. Donc, génial.

117
00:04:15,955 --> 00:04:18,301
Alors Alex, Izzie,
Meredith, Cristina--

118
00:04:18,408 --> 00:04:20,552
